Title: GTEX_data
Description: Gene expression data in normal tissues from GTEx database

Title: CCLE_data
Description: Gene expression data in cancer cell lines from CCLE

Title: normal_tissues_multimapping_data
Description: Gene expression values in normal tissues with or without allowing multimapping

Title: DAC_treated_cells
Description: Gene expression values in a set of cell lines treated or not with 5-Aza-2'-Deoxycytidine (DAC), a demethylating agent

Title: DAC_treated_cells_multimapping
Description: Gene expression values (multimapping allowed) in a set of cell lines treated or not with 5-Aza-2'-Deoxycytidine (DAC)

Title: TCGA_TPM
Description: Gene expression data in TCGA samples

Title: CT_methylation_in_tissues
Description: Methylation values of CpGs located within Cancer-Testis promoters in a set of normal tissues

Title: CT_mean_methylation_in_tissues
Description: Mean methylation values of all CpGs located within Cancer-Testis (CT) promoters in a set of normal tissues

Title: TCGA_CT_methylation
Description: Methylation of CT promoters in TCGA samples

Title: CT_genes
Description: Cancer-Testis (CT) genes description

Title: CCLE_correlation_matrix
Description: Gene correlations in CCLE cancer cell lines

Title: testis_sce
Description: Testis scRNAseq data
DataProvider: The adult human testis transcriptional cell atlas, Guo et al. 2018

Title: scRNAseq_HPA
Description: Gene expression profiles in different human cell types based on scRNAseq data from The Human Protein Atlas

Title: all_genes
Description: All genes description, according to the analysis done for CT genes

Title: FGC_sce
Description: Fetal gonad scRNAseq
DataProvider: Single-cell roadmap of human gonadal development (Garcia-Alonso, Nature 2022)

Title: HPA_cell_type_specificities
Description: Cell type specificities (from HPA)

Title: mean_methylation_in_tissues
Description: Mean methylation values of all CpGs located within all (CT) promoters in a set of normal tissues

Title: methylation_in_tissues
Description: Methylation values of CpGs located within all promoters in a set of normal tissues

Title: oocytes_sce
Description: Oocytes scRNAseq
DataProvider:
NCBI GEO : Decoding dynamic epigenetic landscapes in human oocytes
            using single-cell multi-omics sequencing (Yan et al. Cell Stem Cell 2021)

Title: TCGA_methylation
Description: Methylation of all genes promoters in TCGA samples

Title: embryo_sce_Zhu
Description: Gene expression values in early embryo (blastocyst)
DataProvider: Single Cell DNA Methylome Sequencing of Human Preimplantation Embryos (Zhu et al. 2018)

Title: embryo_sce_Petropoulos
Description: Gene expression values in early embryo (blastocyst and Morula)
DataProvider:
Single-Cell RNA-Seq Reveals Lineage and X Chromosome Dynamics in
            Human Preimplantation Embryos (Petropulous et al, 2014)

Title: hESC_data
Description: Gene expression data in human embryonic stem cells

Title: methylation_in_hESC
Description: Methylation values of CpGs located within all promoters in human embryonic stem cells

Title: mean_methylation_in_hESC
Description: Mean methylation values of all CpGs located within all promoters in human embryonic stem cells

Title: methylation_in_FGC
Description: Methylation values of CpGs located within all promoters in fetal germ cells
DataProvider:
Data from Dissecting the epigenomic dynamics of human fetal germ cell
            development at single-cell resolution (Li et al. 2021)

Title: mean_methylation_in_FGC
Description: Mean methylation values of all CpGs located within all promoters in fetal germ cells
DataProvider:
Data from Dissecting the epigenomic dynamics of human fetal germ cell
            development at single-cell resolution (Li et al. 2021)

Title: methylation_in_embryo
Description: Methylation values of CpGs located within all promoters in early embryo
DataProvider: Single Cell DNA Methylome Sequencing of Human Preimplantation Embryos (Zhu et al. 2018)

Title: mean_methylation_in_embryo
Description: Mean methylation values of all CpGs located within all promoters in early embryo
DataProvider: Single Cell DNA Methylome Sequencing of Human Preimplantation Embryos (Zhu et al. 2018)
